ygData.subject: Re: Questions about making lvl and getting good exp.
ygData.msgSnippet: at level 23 goto rathe mountains and kill unkempt preservers and druids good loot and great xp.  alternate between that and treants.  They counter each others
ygData.messageBody:
at level 23 goto rathe mountains and kill unkempt preservers and druids good
loot and great xp. alternate between that and treants. They counter each
others faction hits.
